# 🇧🇷 Olist E-Commerce Data Analysis

**Signature Project #1 | Data Analytics Learning Journey (Month 01-03)**

---

## 🎯 Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing a real-world Brazilian e-commerce dataset.

The objective is to progressively build strong data analysis skills through:

* Data cleaning (Excel)
* Relational analysis (SQL)
* Visualization (later stages)

---

## 🏗 Data Architecture

The dataset consists of multiple related tables:

* Core tables: `orders`, `order_items`
* Additional tables (future use): `customers`, `products`, `payments`

Work will start with simplified data and progressively move to relational analysis.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack & Methodology

* **Month 01 (Excel):**

  * Data cleaning
  * Table merging (VLOOKUP / Power Query)
  * KPI creation
  * Dashboard building

* **Month 02 (SQL):**

  * Joins between tables
  * Business queries
  * Data modeling basics

* **Month 03 (Python / BI):**

  * Data visualization
  * Final project presentation

